localized.description:
Explore the unconventional decision by Sweden to declare sex as a sport and organize the first-ever European Sex Championship in this thought-provoking video for the UPSC GS1 Indian Society exam. Understand the rationale behind Sweden's unique approach and its implications for societal norms and perceptions of sexuality. Analyze the potential impact on gender equality, sexual empowerment, and the broader discourse on sexual rights. Delve into the debates surrounding the classification of sex as a sport and the controversies associated with such events. Gain insights into the cultural and legal aspects of sexuality in the context of Indian society. Stay informed about the evolving perspectives on sexuality for the UPSC GS1 examination. Watch this video and expand your understanding of the complex dynamics between sex, sports, and societal norms.

snippet.title: Apple WWDC 2023 keynote in 26 minutes
snippet.description:

snippet.title: చంద్రబాబుతో భేటి, అమిత్ షా అసలు వ్యూహం || Amit Shah strategy in meeting Chandra Babu ||
snippet.description:
చంద్రబాబుతో భేటి, అమిత్ షా అసలు వ్యూహం || Amit Shah strategy in meeting Chandra Babu ||
N Chandrababu Naidu meets Shah amid talk of TDP interest in getting back to NDA fold
The BJP leadership has made Telangana the party's focus in its 'Mission South' and has been making inroads in local body elections in the state.
Amid speculation over a regrouping in Andhra Pradesh, TDP chief N Chandrababu Naidu is learnt to have met Union Home Minister and senior BJP leader Amit Shah in the national capital on Saturday.

BJP national president J P Nadda was also present in the meeting, which took place at the Home Minister’s residence here.

In the meeting, which came in the backdrop of speculation over a possible alliance between BJP and its former alliance partner TDP, the leaders are learnt to have discussed the possibility of coming together in Andhra Pradesh, where Naidu’s party is the main opposition, as also in Telangana.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Bollywood Item Songs की सच्चाई देख लो | @SambhavnaSethEntertainment | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Sambhavna Seth’s full name is Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth. We must have seen her on YouTube, in Big Boss, and in many bhojpuri songs. She had a lot of love for dance since childhood. From the very beginning, she wanted to become a heroine. To make a career, she went to Mumbai with her father and gave many auditions, but did not get work and came back to Delhi. She did not do any work for 1 year, then after gaining some confidence, she again came to Mumbai. Got a film after a lot of struggle. She has worked in songs of many big films but those songs did not become hits but everyone was quite impressed with her dance.
Then he got a chance to work in Bhojpuri songs. The first song became so famous that now she started getting a lot of work in the Bhojpuri industry. Time passed and she also appeared in many reality shows like Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi and Desi Girl. Today she runs a YouTube channel named Sambhavna Seth Entertainment on which she posts vlogs.

Today Sambhavna will tell her life story through Josh Talks. So definitely watch this Hindi motivational video of Josh Talks.

Sambhavna Seth जी का पूरा नाम Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth है. हमनें इन्हें YouTube पर, Big Boss में, और कई bhojpuri songs में देखा होगा. बचपन से ही इन्हें Dance से काफ़ी प्यार था. शुरू से ही ये एक Heroine बनना चाहती थीं. Career बनाने के लिए ये अपने पापा के साथ Mumbai गईं कई Auditions दिए लेकिन काम नहीं मिला और ये Delhi वापस आ गई. 1 साल इन्होंने कुछ काम नहीं किया फिर थोड़ा confidence gain करके ये फिर Mumbai आ गई. बहुत struggle के बाद एक film मिली. इन्होंने काफ़ी बड़ी films के songs में काम किया है लेकिन वो गाने hit नहीं हुए लेकिन इनके Dance से सब काफ़ी impressed थे. फिर इन्हें bhojpuri songs में काम करने का मौक़ा मिला. पहला गाना इतना famous हुआ कि अब इन्हें bhojpuri industry में काफ़ी काम मिलने लगा. समय बीतता गया और ये कई reality shows में भी आई जैसे Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi और Desi Girl. आज ये Sambhavna Seth Entertainment नाम से एक YouTube channel चलाती हैं जिसपर ये vlogs डालती हैं. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Sambhavna जी सुनायेंगी अपनी Life story. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi motivational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #SambhavnaSethJoshTalks #SambhavnaSethEntertainment 

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

Then he got a chance to work in Bhojpuri songs. The first song became so famous that now she started getting a lot of work in the Bhojpuri industry. Time passed and she also appeared in many reality shows like Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi and Desi Girl. Today she runs a YouTube channel named Sambhavna Seth Entertainment on which she posts vlogs.

Today Sambhavna will tell her life story through Josh Talks. So definitely watch this Hindi motivational video of Josh Talks.

Sambhavna Seth जी का पूरा नाम Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth है. हमनें इन्हें YouTube पर, Big Boss में, और कई bhojpuri songs में देखा होगा. बचपन से ही इन्हें Dance से काफ़ी प्यार था. शुरू से ही ये एक Heroine बनना चाहती थीं. Career बनाने के लिए ये अपने पापा के साथ Mumbai गईं कई Auditions दिए लेकिन काम नहीं मिला और ये Delhi वापस आ गई. 1 साल इन्होंने कुछ काम नहीं किया फिर थोड़ा confidence gain करके ये फिर Mumbai आ गई. बहुत struggle के बाद एक film मिली. इन्होंने काफ़ी बड़ी films के songs में काम किया है लेकिन वो गाने hit नहीं हुए लेकिन इनके Dance से सब काफ़ी impressed थे. फिर इन्हें bhojpuri songs में काम करने का मौक़ा मिला. पहला गाना इतना famous हुआ कि अब इन्हें bhojpuri industry में काफ़ी काम मिलने लगा. समय बीतता गया और ये कई reality shows में भी आई जैसे Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi और Desi Girl. आज ये Sambhavna Seth Entertainment नाम से एक YouTube channel चलाती हैं जिसपर ये vlogs डालती हैं. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Sambhavna जी सुनायेंगी अपनी Life story. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi motivational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #SambhavnaSethJoshTalks #SambhavnaSethEntertainment 

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं.

snippet.title: S8E6 | Virender Sehwag | Breakfast with Champions ft Gaurav Kapur | @skodaindia     ​
snippet.description:
The season finale of ŠKODA presents Breakfast with Champions ft. Gaurav Kapur has some royal swag! 🏏🌟 Say hello to The Nawab of Najafgarh, The Sultan of Multan. 👑

Virender Sehwag is a born entertainer and he continues to enthrall us with his take on his teammates and stories that are now cricketing folklore. From scooter rides with Ashish Nehra to pranking Sourav Ganguly, and from farm fresh buffalo milk to fine dining that Sachin introduced him to, this episode is a rollercoaster of laughter and nostalgia. 

Hear all about his banter with Shoaib Akhtar and the love he got from Pakistani shopkeepers, the invaluable advice Tiger Pataudi's gave him, how he had to return from the airport before his debut and the epic moment he scored 300 runs with a sensational six!

snippet.title: Odisha Coromandel Express Train Accident Video | యాక్సిడెంట్ ఇలా జరిగింది లైవ్ వీడియో | RTV
snippet.description:
Odisha Coromandel Express Train Accident Video | యాక్సిడెంట్ ఇలా జరిగింది లైవ్ వీడియో | RTV

కోరమాండల్ ఎక్స్‌ప్రెస్ మరియు బెంగళూరు-హౌరా సూపర్‌ఫాస్ట్ ఎక్స్‌ప్రెస్ ప్రమాదం ఎలా జరిగిందో RTV లైవ్ చూపెట్టే ప్రయత్నం చేసింది . కోరమాండల్ ఎక్స్‌ప్రెస్ పశ్చిమ బెంగాల్ మరియు చెన్నైలోని బెంగాల్ షాలిమార్ స్టేషన్ మధ్య నడుస్తుంది. బహనాగా రైల్వే స్టేషన్ సమీపంలో ఈ ఘర్షణ చోటు చేసుకుంది, దీని ఫలితంగా ప్రయాణికులలో గణనీయమైన సంఖ్యలో ప్రాణనష్టం జరిగింది. ఒ

RTV Live tried to show how the Coromandel Express and Bengaluru-Howrah Superfast Express accidents happened. Coromandel Express runs between Bengal Shalimar station in West Bengal and Chennai. The clash took place near Bahanaga railway station, resulting in the loss of a significant number of passengers.

snippet.title: Uncovering the Secrets of Karen Long Neck Village 😱 விசித்திர கிராம மக்கள் 🙊 இவ்ளோ பெரிய கழுத்தா 🤯 ​
snippet.description:
Heyy Deyyss ❤️

Uncovering the Secrets of Karen Long Neck Village |விசித்திர கிராம மக்கள் 😱 இவ்ளோ பெரிய கழுத்தா 🤯 ​ 

We had an extraordinary encounter that left us in awe. We had the chance to witness an incredible experimental creation in the world of entertainment: a combination of a lion and a tiger known as the LIGAR. This magnificent breed is eight times larger than a typical lion or tiger, but despite its immense size, it had a surprising nature, almost like a giant toy.

here are some additional facts about ligers:
- Ligers are the largest known cat species in the world, even larger than their parents, the lion, and the tiger.
- Ligers have a unique appearance, with stripes from the tiger and a mane from the lion.
- Ligers are usually sterile and cannot reproduce, although there have been a few rare cases of ligers being able to mate with other ligers or with lions or tigers.
- Ligers are not found in the wild, as lions and tigers do not share the same habitats in the wild.
- Ligers are often bred in captivity, and there is some controversy surrounding the practice of breeding ligers and other hybrid animals.
- Ligers are known for their playful personalities and are often used in animal shows and attractions.
- Ligers have a lifespan of around 10-15 years, which is shorter than the lifespan of lions and tigers in the

But our adventure didn't stop there! We ventured into a village with a fascinating tradition that caught our attention. In Karen Gong Neck Village, we encountered a community of people known for their unique practice of elongating their necks. These polite and welcoming individuals sustain their livelihood by crafting and selling handmade items. To achieve elongated necks, they gradually add neck rings every four years, resulting in a truly remarkable sight.

here are some interesting facts about Karen Gong Neck Village:

- The Karen Long Neck tribe is originally from Myanmar (Burma) and migrated to Thailand in the 1980s.
- The women of the tribe wear brass rings around their necks, starting at a young age, which give the appearance of elongated necks. Contrary to popular belief, the rings do not actually lengthen the neck but rather push down the collarbone and ribcage to create the illusion of a longer neck.
- The Karen Long Neck tribe is just one of several hill tribes in northern Thailand, each with their own unique culture and traditions.
- The village is located in a mountainous region, surrounded by lush forests and rice paddies.
- Visitors to the village can learn about the tribe's traditional handicrafts, including weaving and embroidery, and purchase handmade souvenirs.
- The village is also home to a school, where children from the tribe can receive an education.
- The Karen Long Neck tribe has faced some controversy and criticism over the years, with some people arguing that the practice of wearing the neck rings is exploitative and objectifying. However, others argue that it is an important part of the tribe's cultural heritage and should be preserved.
- Despite the controversy, Karen Gong Neck Village remains a popular tourist destination, attracting visitors from all over the world who are interested in learning about the tribe's unique culture and traditions.

This captivating journey was filled with astonishing sights and remarkable cultural experiences.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3788 | 3 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3788: Pyarelal's Dilemma
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal gets into trouble as Sapna and Kalpana have accepted his proposal to get married. Earlier Sapna had not revealed her decision while Babita and Madhavi had asked Pyaarelal to accept Kalpana. As everyone discusses the matter at Popatlal's house, Dr. Hathi comes excited to his house. he announces that they have brought him another proposal for marriage. Anjali and Taarak discuss who will tell the truth to Sapna's family, he calls Sapna's mother but she thinks it to be a prank. Keep an eye out! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3788, 3 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Jetha has to leave for America in next three days. Bagha and Nattu Kaka celebrate this and ask Jetha to give them a party. Jetha orders Pizza and French fries for them. He calls Bapuji to tell the news but Nattu Kaka stops him from doing so. Jetha thinks he had such a good day just because of Babita Ji as she told him have a nice day. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of 'Bhide Bana Crorepati':

snippet.title: IAS Suraj Tiwari with Vikas Sir। UPSC Topper 2022। Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Suraj Tiwari has secured 917th rank in the Civil Services Examination 2022. In this video he is sharing his journey of preparation. This video will definitely motivate you.

Team Drishti wishes Suraj a very successful and fruitful career.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 51 Teaser - 1st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: क्या Bhide का Cooker हो गया Blast? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bhide Ka Cooker
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Popatlal is stuck on the balcony. Bhide and Madhavi are stuck outside and are worried about the cooker that is on the gas. Both of them don't have the key. Will Sodhi break the door? Will Daya give some solution? Watch the full episode to find out. Stay tuned to unfold the drama.  

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1993
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of 'Bhide Bana Crorepati':

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 50 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 1st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa
